    RPCRT4.dll!Invoke+0x30
    RPCRT4.dll!NdrStubCall2+0x297

    snip.. snip..

    ole32.dll!StubInvoke+0xa7
    ole32.dll!CCtxComChnl::ContextInvoke+0xe3
